thank you so much for 50k! 🥰✨🫶 let’s celebrate with a #dtiyschallenge !! #bykatiemaidtiys

If you’ve been around for awhile, you know that i like to throw in a little twist to make the challenge more fun. Draw this in your style BUT use a technique you’ve never used before!! 🤩

I chose to use blank space/the white of the paper. Since we’re talking style, this #dtiys challenge is all about experimenting. I can’t wait to see what you come up with!!

Share your artwork with all of us by using #ByKatieMaiDTIYS and comment below what new technique you’ll be using. If you want, tag a friend who you’d like to challenge! I’ll be sharing your artwork on my stories through out the month. There’s no deadline either, so take your time :)

Happy creating xo 

#artchallenge #artwork #artistsoninstagram #illustrationartists #illustragram #artistsoninstagram #artistsupport #artistsupportartists #gouachepainting #gouacheillustration
